  "body": "**About**\nIt's a simple plugin for spigot servers.\nThis plugin blocks crafting\nYou can enable/disable crafting in config.yml.\nYou can add items in the config that can be crafted.\n\n**Commands**\nNo Commands!\n\n**Permissions**\nnocraft.craft (to bypass No Crafting )\n\n**Guide**\n1. Go to your spigot server in the plugins folder.\n2. Put NoCrafting.jar in the plugins folder.\n3. Restart your server.\n4. Enjoy :D\n\n",
